# INSTALLING APPS AND PACKAGES IN LINUX - WITH PARU: 
[git-md-text-formatting-help](https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/writing-on-github/getting-started-with-writing-and-formatting-on-github/basic-writing-and-formatting-syntax)

### Installing paru on your Linux Arch:  
sudo pacman -Sy                 # Update pacman app database!!!  
sudo pacman -S paru             # install paru and its perl dependencies.  

paru --version                  # Check and display paru version info.  

paru -S discover-aur            # adds AUR tab to Discover if you have that "app store" installed.
sudo pacman -S discover flatpak xdg-desktop-portal-kde  # Install Discover App Store if you dont have it!
